<div id="content" class="content wikipage" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<p id="l1">
In magazine and newspaper publishing, a small, text-based ad (set in a small <a title="Point Size" href="Point_Size">point size</a>, commonly one known as <a title="Agate" href="Agate">agate</a>) placed in a lengthy advertising section. Classified ads are often placed by individuals or companies looking for employees, wanting to sell items, rent and/or sell houses and apartments, etc. See also <a title="Display Ad" href="Display_Ad">Display Ad</a>. 
</p>
